{"tid":2410246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"“在中国辦奧運是不道德的” 美眾院共和黨人推出決議籲抵制北京冬奧","createTime":"2021-02-16T12:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T04:49:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9452ff1cdc024aebf7476475a44891f0386b674b","tid":2410246,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"美國國會共和黨聯邦眾議員華爾茲（Rep. Michael Waltz, R-FL）星期一（2月15日）推出決議案，敦促美國應該抵制2022年北京冬季奧運會。 &ldquo;我希望這是美國政府加入180個呼籲抵制（北京冬奧）人權組織的第一步，並讓美國站在世界人權倡導者的前沿，&rdquo;華爾茲議員說。<br />\n<br />\n根據內容，決議案首先敦促美國奧委會向國際奧委會提議將2022年冬奧會轉移到中華人民共和國以外的地點。如果提議遭到國際奧委會的拒絕，&ldquo;美國奧委會和其他國家的奧委會應該退出2022奧運會比賽&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n決議案引用美國國會暨行政當局中國委員會的年度報告稱，中國共產黨去年採取了前所未有的措施，&ldquo;通過審查、恐嚇和拘留行使基本人權的個人和團體來擴大其鎮壓政策，特別是在新疆維吾爾自治區和香港&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n決議提到，中國採取大規模拘留、強迫勞動，以及加大監控力度等手段使中國的宗教受到更嚴格緊密的官方控制。與此同時，決議還指責，中國政府同時以言論審查的方式隱瞞了新冠病毒疫情，進而導致全球大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n決議案稱，&ldquo;奧運會是國際文化的慶典，是人類的節日，旨在將政治、意識形態與外交分歧獨立於外的活動。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;然而，在中國，有組織的暴行仍繼續在新疆進行；香港公民的自由仍持續被踐踏；民眾行使基本權利從事宗教儀式仍受到殘酷迫害；新冠病毒疫情仍在全球肆虐，在中國舉辦2022冬奧會將是不道德、沒有倫理且錯誤的，&rdquo;決議案說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-house-gop-urges-us-to-boycott-2022-bj-winter-olympics-20210216/5780055.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-house-gop-urges-us-to-boycott-2022-bj-winter-olympics-20210216%2F5780055.html&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BRUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=53bc1198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-house-gop-urges-us-to-boycott-2022-bj-winter-olympics-20210216/5780055.html</a>"},{"pid":"a8d5ec4e52a004a03f579a22776869ef201390bb","tid":2410246,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4e722eb86aa1a9b760d93ff7754f4d003e040b","tid":2410246,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"睇下民主黨係人定係妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5f2652b6c913adcc6053de07c1c56670d3affc","tid":2410246,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"兩黨共sick"},{"pid":"d059858bf063d7c0f27758ba4e778bdf22087851","tid":2410246,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5428d85a950fca3eeddc632d7f9dc0b94edfc7bd","tid":2410246,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"All talks, no action"},{"pid":"a4a3521eb02ff1f4ed85d1b80ed8cb1c6dff3afb","tid":2410246,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db4e722eb86aa1a9b760d93ff7754f4d003e040b","tid":2410246,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"睇下民主黨係人定係妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T02:38:34.000Z","msg":"Ted Cruz 都唔支持，共和黨都唔會好多人支持啦，何况民主黨。"},{"pid":"fe5cb34d21f447a1bfa961d5d92f22a7a82b3537","tid":2410246,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a992eed1364d4cedf3500f11a566294569c0b4","tid":2410246,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}